folder: West End Avenue & 84th Street (West), Manhattan, NY
text:
505 West End Avenue at N.W. corner of 84th Street, a newly built apartment house replacing the original old residences built on the site between 1891 and 1897. The small house adjoining is
511 West End Avenue.
The building on the N.E. corner, a little of which is shown to the right of the picture, was erected between 1910 and 1916.
1922.
Gift of E. M. Jenks.
